## Token handling (Flutter client)

The SDK attaches the JWT to every Supabase request automatically. Do not write custom refresh logic.

```dart
// ✅ Read the live token when forwarding to an Edge Function
final token = supabase.auth.currentSession?.accessToken;
if (token == null) throw Exception('User not authenticated');
headers['Authorization'] = 'Bearer $token';

// ❌ Never cache the JWT string across async gaps
// ❌ Never hardcode a JWT
const token = 'eyJhb...'; // FORBIDDEN
```

