## Edge Function client setup

Use the factory helpers from `supabase/ref/supabase.ts`:

```typescript
// Admin operations (bypasses RLS) — use only when elevated privilege is required
const supabase = getSupabaseClient();

// Act as the calling user (respects RLS) — prefer this for user data
const supabase = createSupabaseClientWithAuth(token);
```

